of CanUlc 537 and fire alarm inspections ensured the highest standards of safety and compliance.<\/p>\n<p>Now as a valued technical sales rep, Bernard quotes maintenance and fit-ups for projects of all sizes. He also provides project management and technical support for inspections, service, and engineering departments. His explicit knowledge of Automatic Fire Protection codes ensures that every project meets stringent safety standards.<\/p>\n<p>Furthermore, his extensive experience, commitment to teaching and mentorship make him a valuable asset. Colleagues benefit from immediate technical expertise, whether it involves code-related questions, installation methods, or troubleshooting complex issues.<\/p>\n<p>In fact, one of Bernard&#8217;s standout qualities is his passion for problem-solving. Dropping everything to assist colleagues, tackling technical challenges head-on, and finding innovative solutions are not just part of the job; they are the aspects he most enjoys.<\/p>\n<p>In conclusion, Bernard&#8217;s entrepreneurial spirit, and solution-driven approach continue to set him apart as an innovator in his field. His Algonquin heritage shines through in his work, and personal life, for example in his spiritual practices, and his passion for hunting and fishing.<\/p>\n<p>As a matter of fact, t<span tabindex=\"0\" role=\"tooltip\"><span class=\"c5aZPb\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-enable-toggle-animation=\"true\" data-extra-container-classes=\"ZLo7Eb\" data-hover-hide-delay=\"1000\" data-hover-open-delay=\"500\" data-send-open-event=\"true\" data-theme=\"0\" data-width=\"250\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjbrfn-hOiGAxUXpIkEHZnJA38QmpgGegQIGBAD\"><span class=\"JPfdse\" data-bubble-link=\"\" data-segment-text=\"Algonquin\">he Algonquin<\/span><\/span><\/span> Philosophy is: <em>Remain close to the Great Spirit. Show great respect for your fellow beings. Work together for the benefit of all Mankind. Give assistance and kindness whenever needed.<\/em> Indeed, Bernard&#8217;s dedication to resolving issues, and delivering excellence in fire protection, reflects a deep commitment to the craft and to the success of his Viking Ottawa team.<\/p>\n<h3>Attracting the Best Talent in the Industry<\/h3>\n<p>At Viking, we take pride in employing the most qualified sprinkler fitters in the industry. We value and reward our outstanding specialists, reflecting a high employee retention rate.<\/p>\n<p>By choosing a career as a sprinkler fitter at Viking, you gain access to extensive expertise and solid professional guidance from our staff. We employ top technicians, recognized across Canada, who share their skills to shape the next generation of experts.<\/p>\n<p>Photo: Bernard St-Aubin, Senior Technical Sales Representative, and the Viking Fire Protection Ottawa Team<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9081\" title=\"Technical Sales Rep with Sprinkler Fitter Expertise Viking#1\" src=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-content\/smush-webp\/2024\/06\/ottawa-office-team-inside-1-300x223.png.webp\" alt=\"Technical Sales Rep with Sprinkler Fitter Expertise Viking#1\" width=\"781\" height=\"580\" srcset=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-content\/smush-webp\/2024\/06\/ottawa-office-team-inside-1-300x223.png.webp 300w, https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-content\/smush-webp\/2024\/06\/ottawa-office-team-inside-1-768x571.png.webp 768w, https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/ottawa-office-team-inside-1.png 1022w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 781px) 100vw, 781px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Join the Best<\/h3>\n<p>Bernard emphasizes the importance of hands-on experience on construction sites. He acknowledges that practical experience, on a diversity of projects, is essential and cannot be solely acquired in the classroom.<\/p>\n<p>Moreover, he attributes part of his success to being assigned to a diversity of large scale and specialized fire protection projects: from chemical plants and hangars to office towers and residential buildings. Bernard&#8217;s experience spans various environments, each with unique challenges and requirements and working with the expertise of the Viking Ottawa team, which has enabled him to progress in his career to this level of achievement.<\/p>\n<p>If you have completed your sprinkler fitter training and wish to enhance your skills and develop your professional experience with the best technicians in the industry, visit our careers page and <a href=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/join-the-team\/\">contact us<\/a> today.<\/p>\n<p>At Viking Fire Protection, you will find a work environment that fosters your professional development and allows you to become tomorrow&#8217;s expert.<\/p>\n<p>For 90 years, our strong reputation has been built on our commitment to providing top-notch fire protection products and services, that perfectly meet our clients&#8217; requirements.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/job\/\">Apply today<\/a> and join one of the most respected fire protection companies in Canada!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A Path of Dedication and Excellence in Fire Protection At Viking Fire Protection, we believe in showcasing our dedicated workforce. We are proud to be the employer of choice for the industry&#8217;s most experienced and knowledgeable fire protection professionals. Because we value our exceptional team, we are dedicating a special segment of our blog, the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":9349,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[43],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-9011","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-employee-stories","cf"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vikingfire.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9011","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https